  author = {Sakschewski, Boris and Caesar, Levke and Andersen, Lauren and Bechthold, Max and Bergfeld, Lotta and Beusen, Arthur and Billing, Maik and Bodirsky, Benjamin Leon and Botsyun, Svetlana and Dennis, Donovan P. and Donges, Jonathan and Dou, Xinyu and Eriksson, Axel and Fetzer, Ingo and Gerten, Dieter and Häyhä, Tiina and Hebden, Sophie and Heckmann, Tim and Heilemann, Adrian and Huiskamp, Willem and Jahnke, Annika and Kaiser, Jonas and Kitzmann, Niklas H. and Krönke, Jonathan and Kühnel, Dana and Laureanti, Nicole C. and Li, Chaohui and Liu, Zhu and Loriani, Sina and Ludescher, Josef and Mathesius, Sabine and Norström, Albert and Otto, Friederike and Paolucci, Anja and Pokhotelov, Dimitry and Rafiezadeh Shahi, Kasra and Raju, Emmanuel and Rostami, Masoud and Schaphoff, Sibyll and Schmidt, Christian and Steinert, Norman J. and Stenzel, Fabian and Virkki, Vili and Wendt-Potthoff, Katrin and Wunderling, Nico and Rockström, Johan and Kitzmann, Niklas Henrik and Caesar, Levke and Sakschewski, Boris and Rockström, Johan},
